<view class="card gap">
  <view style="font-weight:600">WebDAV 配置</view>
  <view>
    <text class="label">服务器地址</text>
    <input class="input" placeholder="https://dav.jianguoyun.com/dav/" value="{{cfg.url}}" data-field="url" bindinput="onField" />
  </view>
  <view>
    <text class="label">账号</text>
    <input class="input" value="{{cfg.username}}" data-field="username" bindinput="onField" />
  </view>
  <view>
    <text class="label">密码 / 应用授权密码</text>
    <input class="input" password value="{{cfg.password}}" data-field="password" bindinput="onField" />
  </view>
  <view>
    <text class="label">远程子目录 (需在网盘里预先建好)</text>
    <input class="input" value="{{cfg.remote_dir}}" data-field="remote_dir" bindinput="onField" />
  </view>
  <button class="btn btn-secondary" bindtap="saveCfg">保存配置</button>
  <view class="muted">小程序受微信限制不能自动建目录，请先在网盘里手动创建该文件夹。</view>
  <view class="muted">🔐 加密：{{cfg.passphrase ? '已开启 (在「设置」页配置口令)' : '未加密 (可在「设置」页设口令)'}}</view>
</view>

<view class="card row" style="gap:16rpx">
  <button class="btn btn-primary" style="flex:1" disabled="{{busy}}" bindtap="doBackup">立即备份</button>
  <button class="btn btn-secondary" style="flex:1" disabled="{{busy}}" bindtap="refresh">刷新列表</button>
</view>
<view wx:if="{{msg}}" class="card"><text class="{{msg[0]==='❌' ? 'err' : 'ok'}}">{{msg}}</text></view>

<view class="card">
  <view style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8rpx">备份历史</view>
  <view wx:if="{{backups.length === 0}}" class="muted">暂无备份（点「刷新列表」或「立即备份」）。</view>
  <view wx:for="{{backups}}" wx:key="name" style="padding:14rpx 0;border-top:1rpx solid #f1f5f9">
    <view class="break">{{item.name}}</view>
    <view class="row between" style="margin-top:6rpx">
      <text class="muted">{{item.sizeText}} · {{item.created_at}}</text>
      <view class="row" style="gap:20rpx">
        <text style="color:#047857" data-name="{{item.name}}" bindtap="restore">恢复</text>
        <text style="color:#b91c1c" data-name="{{item.name}}" bindtap="del">删除</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
